% Verification
```bash
pytest -q tests/test_user_story_tests.py tests/test_contract_check.py tests/test_coverage_contracts.py tests/commands/test_analysis.py
pytest -q tests/test_contract_check.py::TestRealPromptLegacySafety::test_bundled_prompts_no_errors
pylint pdd/user_story_tests.py
```
Public helpers use module-level `# pylint: disable=too-many-arguments` (and related)
on their definitions; the pylint command above should exit 0.
